DWFToolkit::DWFPackageVersion60Extension

DWFToolkit::DWFPackageVersion60Extension Class Reference
[DWF Package API]

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This is the DWF 6.0 File Format plug-in for the DWFPackageWriter.

Since:
7.1.0
The current DWF Format version is 6.11. This version extension allows DWF 6.0 files to be created. DWF 6.0 files can have ePlot sections only.
